  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/94a5d9160733ddb4612b42f8344159d7.avif?t=1726096186\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>A new adventure in ancient Greece!</strong></u></h2>In a world shaken by the fall of Atlantis, the children of Ares unite to stop their father from destroying everything that's left, but to do so they will have to discover what can be so strong that it challenges even the immortality of a god.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/64b012080fae7aefb43c698e940f81be.avif?t=1726096186\" width=600 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Be the god of fear</u></strong></h2>Play as Phobos, the Greek god of fear, avoid traps, and fight your enemies using fear as your greatest weapon.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/11eab8fd599ca14a7efdb531dabc4bb7.apng?t=1726096186\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/11eab8fd599ca14a7efdb531dabc4bb7.poster.avif?t=1726096186\" class=\"bb_img\" width=180 height=180 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/64b012080fae7aefb43c698e940f81be.avif?t=1726096186\" width=600 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Face your enemies</u></strong></h2>Discover how to face more than 15 different types of enemies, skeletons, ghosts, constructs, witches, Spartan warriors, and more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/fdfd7baf64ef79d4710ebeafefe901be.poster.avif?t=1726096186\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/fdfd7baf64ef79d4710ebeafefe901be.webm?t=1726096186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/64b012080fae7aefb43c698e940f81be.avif?t=1726096186\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/129a4dfedc79b162f04d327fea84f5bb.avif?t=1726096186\" width=600 height=600 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/94a5d9160733ddb4612b42f8344159d7.avif?t=1726096186\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>A new adventure in ancient Greece!</strong></u></h2>In a world shaken by the fall of Atlantis, the children of Ares unite to stop their father from destroying everything that's left, but to do so they will have to discover what can be so strong that it challenges even the immortality of a god.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/64b012080fae7aefb43c698e940f81be.avif?t=1726096186\" width=600 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Be the god of fear</u></strong></h2>Play as Phobos, the Greek god of fear, avoid traps, and fight your enemies using fear as your greatest weapon.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/11eab8fd599ca14a7efdb531dabc4bb7.apng?t=1726096186\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/11eab8fd599ca14a7efdb531dabc4bb7.poster.avif?t=1726096186\" class=\"bb_img\" width=180 height=180 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/64b012080fae7aefb43c698e940f81be.avif?t=1726096186\" width=600 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Face your enemies</u></strong></h2>Discover how to face more than 15 different types of enemies, skeletons, ghosts, constructs, witches, Spartan warriors, and more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835430/extras/fdfd